en: I've been watching your episodes. Nice Job. Good Ratings.
I saw you got some blueprints on your last run.
Sweet. Im *name*, the lead engineer of the team making all of your gear.
Vee decided it would be good TV if you had something to find. So they decided to spread them around the set.
Well anyways, now that I have that, I'll get to work.
Ah, the &4Debug Sword&r, this was supposed to be a  secret, oh well, don’t make blueprints for what you don’t want to be found I guess.
As I was saying… The blueprints you picked up, &acan I have them?
[TEMP] Ahem. Vee spread blueprints around as an incentive.
Well actually, you don’t have any. Huh. I could have swore I saw some.
